    <br/><br/>
    <h2 class="normal custom-h2">Adding new content to Popular Resources</h2>
    <p class='lead'>
      To add new content in the Popular Resources section (figure 1), go to the CMS Dashboard – Resources – Add New (figure 2). Be sure to select a <b>User</b>, check <b>featured</b>, uncheck <b>Inactive</b> and then select a <b>windows type</b>.
      In the field labeled “Kind”, write in the one that best suits your post: <br /><br />

       Resource <br />
       Template <br />
       Scholarship <br />
       Toolkit <br />
       Form <br />
       Handout<br />

    </p>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
