    <p class='lead'>
      To add new content in the Latest News section (figure 1), go to the CMS Dashboard – Resource – Add New and add all new content.
      Make sure to select the “Featured” check box and write the word “Story” in the Kind field.
      Save all changes by selecting the Save button at the bottom of the page.
