    <p class='lead'>
      Then you should add a new "Workshop Resources" record to associate the Leader Spotlight to a workshop, go to the CMS Dashboard – Workshop Resource – Add New and add all new content, first find the workshop that you want to associate the leader spotlight using the workshop selector (start typing the name) and then find the already created leader spotlight resource using the "resource" selector (start typing the name), then click save.
    </p>

